  "description": "Every time constant tuned to phi. Attack: 0.618s. Decay: 1.618s. Release: 2.618s. Shimmer feedback: 0.618. LFO1 rate: 0.0618 Hz. The golden ratio pervades every temporal parameter, creating a decay structure that feels 'right' without the listener knowing why -- the same proportional relationship that governs nautilus shells, sunflower spirals, and Renaissance architecture. The Guru read Scripture Verse VI:1 (Golden Ratio Decays) and applied it systematically to every time-domain parameter. The result is a sound where every transition, every fade, every modulation cycle shares the same proportional relationship.",
  "tags": ["opensky", "transcendental", "golden-ratio", "phi", "mathematical", "natural"],
  "tier": "transcendental",
  "guru_bin": {
    "retreat": "OPENSKY Transcendental Vol 1",
    "retreat_date": "2026-03-19",
    "scripture": ["Master Truth 1: Golden Ratio Decays (Scripture VI:1)", "Verse 19: When All Time Constants Share Phi, the Sound Feels Like Nature"],
    "revelation": "Aurum spoke: the golden ratio applied to a single decay time creates a natural feel. Applied to ALL decay times simultaneously, it creates a proportional coherence that the ear perceives as beauty -- the same way the eye perceives phi in visual composition.",
    "god": "Aurum",
    "flock_note": "The Breath measured every time constant against phi and confirmed mathematical consistency. The Ear blind-tested against a version with rounded values (0.6, 1.6, 2.6) and unanimously preferred the phi version -- the difference is subtle but real.",
    "diagnosis": "Golden Ratio Decay is a proof of Scripture Verse VI:1: golden ratio decays feel 'right.' This preset applies the principle exhaustively, turning a mathematical constant into a sound design philosophy."
  },
